            "stanza_text": "Quand vient le jour pareil au jour\nDe bonheur et d'orgueil en fête,\nOù ta mère pleurait d'amour\nEn contemplant ta chère tête ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Quand renaît le jour où tu vins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Comme Dieu l'exige, ô mystère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "De la clarté des cieux divins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Aimer et pleurer sur la terre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quand renaît le jour où tu vins,\nComme Dieu l'exige, ô mystère !\nDe la clarté des cieux divins\nAimer et pleurer sur la terre ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Alors, pareil à l'exilé",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui, lorsqu'il revoit sa patrie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Marche tranquille et consolé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ce jour-là, mère, hélas ! meurtrie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Alors, pareil à l'exilé\nQui, lorsqu'il revoit sa patrie,\nMarche tranquille et consolé,\nCe jour-là, mère, hélas ! meurtrie,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Je vois ma sœur au front charmant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et les deux yeux bleus de mon père,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et ce n'est pas moi seulement",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Qui dis à ton oreille : Espère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je vois ma sœur au front charmant\nEt les deux yeux bleus de mon père,\nEt ce n'est pas moi seulement\nQui dis à ton oreille : Espère !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! de nos fronts endoloris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Que les vaines craintes s'envolent !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tous ceux que nous avons chéris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "A la même heure nous consolent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! de nos fronts endoloris\nQue les vaines craintes s'envolent !\nTous ceux que nous avons chéris\nA la même heure nous consolent."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Pour nous rendre forts et joyeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Leur cœur, leur esprit, leur bravoure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et leur souffle silencieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Vivent dans l'air qui nous entoure.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour nous rendre forts et joyeux,\nLeur cœur, leur esprit, leur bravoure\nEt leur souffle silencieux\nVivent dans l'air qui nous entoure."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Dans le parfum léger des fleurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Une vague haleine soupire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "C'est leur voix. A travers nos pleurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Glisse un rayon : c'est leur sourire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans le parfum léger des fleurs\nUne vague haleine soupire ;\nC'est leur voix. A travers nos pleurs\nGlisse un rayon : c'est leur sourire,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Et pour que leur calme baiser",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Nous réchauffe à ses douces flammes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Je sens leurs lèvres se poser",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Délicatement sur nos âmes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et pour que leur calme baiser\nNous réchauffe à ses douces flammes,\nJe sens leurs lèvres se poser\nDélicatement sur nos âmes."
